arted and the application is already installed. In addition to the ones available in the marketplace, you can create your own images, stored as Amazon Machine Images (AMIs). This may be nec- essary if a company has its own application, developed in-house, that needs to run. Once there is an AMI, multiple instances of that image can be spun up as needed.
